    &bootloader
    &kp GRAV     &kp NUM_1  &kp NUM_2 &kp NUM_3  &kp NUM_4  &kp NUM_5   &kp PSCRN           &kp PAUSE_BREAK  &kp NUM_6  &kp NUM_7    &kp NUM_8    &kp NUM_9   &kp NUM_0   &mt LCTL MINUS
